ic/report-shows-disaster-facing-grassroots-music-venues-the-big-companies-and-arenas-are-now-going-to-have-to-answer-for-this-3576307">MVT进一步<em> </em>报道称，草根音乐场馆面临着一场“灾难”</a> ，要求对更大的场馆征收门票税和更广泛的行业进行投资的呼声越来越高。</p><p> “最具挑战性的一年”的一些重要发现包括发现 125 个英国场馆放弃现场音乐表演，其中一半以上完全关闭。据报道，场馆面临的其他压力包括能源价格飙升、租金上涨、供应成本、营业费率、许可问题、 <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manchester-night-day-cardiff-fuel-post-lockdown-noise-complaints-venues-3103934">噪音投诉</a>和<a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-venue-trust-thank-help-gigs-return-2021-2842425">COVID-19 的持续冲击波</a>。</p><p>自该报告发布以来， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/budget-slammed-as-a-missed-opportunity-by-uk-live-music-industry-3598110">MVT 猛烈抨击英国政府预算，称其“错失了机会”</a> ，因为没有削减门票增值税。</p><p>夜间产业协会 (NTIA) 还发现， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/31-per-cent-of-uk-nightclubs-closed-last-year-as-industry-demands-government-action-3587334">去年有 31% 的英国夜总会关闭，</a>平均每周关闭两家夜总会。</p><p>其他消息中，利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 将为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-oasis-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-uk-tour-dates-tickets-3515369">“Definitely Maybe” 30 周年纪念日进行完整巡演</a>- <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/liam-gallagher-tickets/artist/2055477?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=WyQS5CymqxyNU6mQdCxfu1IQUkHUm4TIb08n0s0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559">在此</a>查找门票并查看下面的日期。</p><p> <strong>2024 年 6 月</strong><br /><strong>02 – 谢菲尔德，Utilita Arena</strong><br /> <strong>03 – 卡迪夫，Utilita Arena</strong><br /> <strong>06 – 伦敦，O2</strong><br /> <strong>07 – 伦敦，O2</strong><br /> <strong>10 – 伦敦，O2</strong><br /> <strong